  "title": "Sales Support Executive (Japanese Speaking) #80259",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction Industrial Machinery</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Support Executive (Japanese Speaking)</strong></li><li>Working Location: West - Tuas Crescent (Company transport provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon-Fri: 8 am-5 pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 5,000 + Travel Allowance + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive market expansion and identify new business opportunities in Southeast Asia</li><li>Undertake frequent business travel within Southeast Asia as per request</li><li>Manage customer accounts and maintain strong, long-term business relationships</li><li>Oversee customer sales activities, marketing meetings, and reporting</li><li>Provide administrative and logistical support during client visits</li><li>Handle customer inquiries and resolve issues in a professional and timely manner</li><li>Prepare internal and external documents, reports, and communications</li><li>Prepare proposals and application documents in Japanese, ensuring accuracy and clarity</li><li>Perform other related tasks or duties as assigned by management</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. 1 year of experience in Sales & Marketing in the Construction/Engineering field</li><li>Flexible to travel in short notice for oversea business trips when required</li><li>Proficient in both written and spoken Japanese and English, with the ability to adapt communication style to effectively engage with Japanese-speaking clients</li><li>Proficiency in MS office</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80259 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
